    <item>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://androiddev.social/@ashdavies/116693981461703637</guid>
      <link>https://androiddev.social/@ashdavies/116693981461703637</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 21:34:07 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p class="quote-inline"&gt;RE: &lt;a href="https://mastodon.scot/@LaChasseuse/116692474272148212" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;mastodon.scot/@LaChasseuse/116&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;692474272148212&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is probably true, though the truth is much more complicated, societies have made themselves dependent on oil, so the infrastructure is still there, switching to renewable energy (whilst I wholeheartedly agree is the correct choice) takes time, and significant investment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;True, but paints &amp;quot;if we just switched&amp;quot; as an easy option.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is our only option.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
