      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 13:10:44 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;It&amp;#39;s absolutely shocking that German restaurants can hire lawyers to make Google take down any local reviews that aren&amp;#39;t 5 stars.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;#39;ve had a take-down notice for a 3-star review for what was a fairly average burger place. I could try to contest it, but without going to court it would likely amount to nothing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Don&amp;#39;t believe Google Maps ratings in Germany.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
